snippet.title: LYMBUS Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter LYMBUS, Q1 2024. Wishlist now at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2683590/LYMBUS

Descend into a digital labyrinth of our own making. Move around with your keys. Do everything else with your cards. Exercise maximum strategy in building your deck, then throw it out the window in screen-shaking, bullet hell-style battles. Combat happens in real time, meaning every moment matters.
